{"tid":1063669,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【港人集體回憶】卡拉屋企遇《閃電傳真機》 蓋世寶麥包譚玉瑛老友聚會","createTime":"2019-03-16T03:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T07:32:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"79745b80e723a9219d04c3333b007d33f7532579","tid":1063669,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:02:32.000Z","msg":"兒童節目《閃電傳真機》當年接替1980年《430穿梭機》播出，陪伴港人成長，後來被《至NET小人類》取代，譚玉瑛主持兒童節目超過32年，今年是《閃電傳真機》步入首播30周年。<br />\n蓋世寶今日上載與《閃電傳真機》主持譚玉瑛、麥長青、黎芷珊等的合照，蓋世寶留言：「今晚實在是一個輕鬆又愉快的聚餐！還巧遇多位前輩呢。芷珊姐姐生日快樂啊！」他們是為3月1日53歲的芷珊姐姐補祝生日。<br />\n《閃電傳真機》一眾成員在台式火鍋店遇上90年代經典處境劇《卡拉屋企》演員吳鎮宇、鄭敬基、楚原、盧宛茵及黎海珊（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Ck4taU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Ck4taU&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnD9kuezr8BQg8uGmIe3q97E%3D&h=6d4c68a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Ck4taU</a> ），原來他們在同一地點相約食飯，眾人開心影大合照，而鎮宇他們正為「肥媽」盧宛茵慶祝66歲生日。<br />\n《蘋果》今日致電麥長青（麥包），他說﹕「能約到相聚已難得，因各自也有工作在身，未必配合到，好似阿Ben正在加拿大拍緊嘢，所以能見面已很開心，大家講講近況，傾傾動向，無所不談，這才是老友聚會。咁啱遇到他們所以一齊合照留念！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190315/large/1552644027_3403.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190315%2Flarge%2F1552644027_3403.jpg&h=3e4b199b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190315/large/1552644169_843f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190315%2Flarge%2F1552644169_843f.jpg&h=639007fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190315/large/1552644169_7378.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190315%2Flarge%2F1552644169_7378.jpg&h=0ff458bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190315/large/1552644274_37f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190315%2Flarge%2F1552644274_37f9.jpg&h=d41b359e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190315/large/1552644169_b5f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190315%2Flarge%2F1552644169_b5f7.jpg&h=b70a1e04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190315/59373146\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190315%2F59373146&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnD9kuezr8BQg8uGmIe3q97E%3D&h=2b831f2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190315%2F59373146&h=e432d1fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190315/59373146</a>"},{"pid":"597b7c56656f2e17e24fabd50a39e541388fd552","tid":1063669,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:40:04.000Z","msg":"卡拉屋企隻狗呢"},{"pid":"99201460325fc3328628984a3e0f02e8190d065e","tid":1063669,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"597b7c56656f2e17e24fabd50a39e541388fd552","tid":1063669,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:40:04.000Z","msg":"卡拉屋企隻狗呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:56:46.000Z","msg":"無睇鬚根show?"},{"pid":"c0a0f937732c801d5d1a5cbdd8b1d5cf8253397c","tid":1063669,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99201460325fc3328628984a3e0f02e8190d065e","tid":1063669,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"597b7c56656f2e17e24fabd50a39e541388fd552","tid":1063669,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:40:04.000Z","msg":"卡拉屋企隻狗呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:56:46.000Z","msg":"無睇鬚根show?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:2